This is the README file for the libcapcomm package.

This software comes with ABSOLUTELY NO WARRANTY.  See the file COPYING for
details.

Libcapcomm is a C++ library for reading and generating Common Alerting
Protocol [CAP] messages. It aims toward compliance with CAP v1.2.

Information regarding CAP can be found at:
    https://docs.oasis-open.org/emergency/cap/v1.2/CAP-v1.2-os.pdf
